OL,3,CCity's Debenhams to be knocked down to
OL,4,Cbuild tower of 'affordable' flats
OL,6,FPlans to demolish a derelict
OL,7,Fdepartment store for new tower blocks
OL,8,Fin Bristol city centre have been
OL,9,Fapproved.
OL,11,FDebenhams has laid empty for three
OL,12,Fyears, but will now be knocked down to
OL,13,Fmake way for 502 new flats.
OL,15,FThe developer now has planning
OL,16,Fpermission from Bristol City Council
OL,17,Ffor their major scheme on the
OL,18,FHorsefair by the Bearpit roundabout.
