OL,3,CCity's Debenhams to be knocked down to
OL,4,Cbuild tower of 'affordable' flats
OL,6,FThe flats - 100 of which "affordable"-
OL,7,F will be housed in several buildings
OL,8,Fincluding a 28 storey tower block.
OL,10,FMore than 100 people objected to the
OL,11,Fplans, largely due to the height of
OL,12,Fthe tallest tower.
OL,14,FSeveral urged the development control
OL,15,Fcommittee on 24 April to refuse
OL,16,Fpermission, due to the perceived harm
OL,17,Fto views across the city centre, and
OL,18,Floss of the 1950s department store.
