OL,3,CCity's Debenhams to be knocked down to
OL,4,Cbuild tower of 'affordable' flats
OL,6,FIn response, Charlie Royle, director
OL,7,Fof developer 33 Horsefair Ltd, said:
OL,8,F"Bristol faces an enormous housing
OL,9,Fcrisis.
OL,11,F"For this site, a housing-led mixed
OL,12,Fuse redevelopment is the only answer.
OL,13,FWe're proposing more than 500 new
OL,14,Fhomes, set along a tree-lined
OL,15,Fpedestrian retail street. One hundred
OL,16,Fof those homes will be affordable.
OL,26,@pD@AOUsD@AOU
