OL,3,CCity's Debenhams to be knocked down to
OL,4,Cbuild tower of 'affordable' flats
OL,6,F"Our proposal would repurpose the site
OL,7,Finto a green, attractive, safe, and
OL,8,Fvibrant place to live, work and
OL,9,Fsocialise, with an additional #11
OL,10,Fmillion a year spending going towards
OL,11,Fthe struggling Broadmead."
OL,13,FDebenhams closed down in 2021 after
OL,14,Fthe company went into administration.
OL,16,FOver half the flats will have windows
OL,17,Fon only one side, with nine per cent
OL,18,Fof the flats being both single aspect
OL,19,Fand north-facing, creating concerns
OL,20,Fabout a lack of sunlight.
