OL,3,CCity's Debenhams to be knocked down to
OL,4,Cbuild tower of 'affordable' flats
OL,6,FOther concerns included the potential
OL,7,Ffor strong winds along the north
OL,8,Fstreet, with the new tall towers
OL,9,Fcreating a canyon effect.
OL,11,FAt 28 storeys tall, the tower block
OL,12,Fwill be one of the tallest buildings
OL,13,Fin Bristol.
OL,15,FCouncillors on the committee were
OL,16,Fsplit about the plans.
OL,18,FA majority voted in favour of the new
OL,19,Fhomes, while Greens voted against the
OL,20,Fplans.
